Apache Sqoop 1.4.7 Installation in Hadoop 

Step 1:  wget https://archive.apache.org/dist/sqoop/1.4.7/sqoop-1.4.7.bin__hadoop-2.6.0.tar.gz
Step 2:  tar -xzf sqoop-1.4.7.bin__hadoop-2.6.0.tar.gz
Step 3:  mv sqoop-1.4.7.bin__hadoop-2.6.0 sqoop
Step 4:  Add below two lines in .bashrc

vi .bashrc

$export SQOOP_HOME=/home/cloudadmin/sqoop
$export PATH=$PATH:$SQOOP_HOME/bin

:wq!

Step 5: source .bashrc
Step 6: cd sqoop/conf/; cp sqoop-env-template.sh sqoop-env.sh
Step 7: 
